OL,3,CInterim Commissioner for Standards
OL,4,Cappointed after resignation
OL,6,FMr Ozanne was unanimously chosen by
OL,7,Fthe Committee following a shortlisting
OL,8,Fand interview process.
OL,10,FDeputy Sarah Hansmann Rouxel,
OL,11,FPresident of SACC, explains: "We were
OL,12,Fencouraged both by the number of
OL,13,Fresponses we received and by the very
OL,14,Fhigh calibre of candidates who came
OL,15,Fforward.
OL,17,F"The Committee was keen to ensure that
OL,18,Fthe duties of the Commissioner for
OL,19,FStandards could continue to be carried
OL,20,Fout independently and effectively
OL,21,Fduring this period of review.
