OL,3,CInterim Commissioner for Standards
OL,4,Cappointed after resignation
OL,6,F"Mr Andrew Ozanne brings a great deal
OL,7,Fof relevant experience in
OL,8,Fadjudication, complaints handling, and
OL,9,Fprofessional discipline."
OL,11,FThe new interim Commissioner has
OL,12,Fpreviously served as a non-States
OL,13,Fmember within the former Home
OL,14,FDepartment and as President of Chambre
OL,15,Fde Discipline of the Guernsey Bar,
OL,16,Fwhich oversees the conduct of legal
OL,17,Fprofessionals.
OL,19,FHe also holds an OBE for services to
OL,20,Fthe community.
